==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kibitka
<hw>Ki*bit"ka</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Kibitkas</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Russ.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A tent used by the Kirghiz Tartars.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A rude kind of Russian vehicle, on wheels or on
runners, sometimes covered with cloth or leather, and often used as a
movable habitation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kiblah</ent>⟦br⟧
